---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Infinite Reality">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Infinite Reality</h1>
      <p class="text-xl themed-text-secondary leading-relaxed">There's a shape that persistent things share. We keep finding it—at the bottom of mathematics, inside ancient philosophy, written in tree rings. It's the same shape every time.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- The Shape -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">The Shape</h2>
      <div class="themed-text-secondary space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
        <p>Everything that persists seems to do so by circulating around something it can't occupy.</p>

        <p>The hurricane wraps its fury around a still eye. The tree adds rings around a center that can rot away completely—and keeps standing. Try to catch the present moment and you'll chase it forever. Try to find the "you" that's looking and you'll orbit the question indefinitely.</p>

        <p>We're not the first to notice. Euler wrote it in five symbols: <span class="font-mono">e<sup>iπ</sup> + 1 = 0</span>. Ancient Chinese observers compressed it into the opening of the Dao De Jing. Trees write it in wood every year.</p>

        <p class="themed-text-muted">Same shape. Different notations.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Grammar -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">The Grammar</h2>
      <div class="themed-text-secondary space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
        <p>We call it the Recursive Structural Model. Three requirements for persistence:</p>

        <div class="themed-surface border rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
          <p class="mb-3"><strong>Contrast</strong> — Opposites must exist for anything to be distinguishable.</p>
          <p class="mb-3"><strong>Rotation</strong> — Those opposites can't just sit there frozen; they have to orbit each other, stay in motion.</p>
          <p><strong>Closure</strong> — The orbit has to complete, has to come back, or it just spirals away into nothing.</p>
        </div>

        <p>That's it. That's the grammar of persistence. The generative center falls out as geometric consequence—you can't occupy it, but everything organizes around it.</p>

        <p class="themed-text-muted italic">We're not proving anything. We're pointing at what's already there.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Before You Dive In -->
    <section class="mb-16 themed-surface border rounded-lg p-6">
      <p class="themed-text-secondary mb-4">Before you dive in, you might want to know: <a href="/confidence" style="color: var(--color-accent);">How solid is this?</a></p>
      <p class="themed-text-muted text-sm">We've mapped our confidence levels—what we're sure of, what we're guessing, and how this could all be wrong.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Where to Start -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Where to Start</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/essays" class="block rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors text-center" style="background: var(--color-accent); color: white;">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Selected Essays</p>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-90">Pick whatever catches your eye. Human-friendly entry points.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/catalog" class="block themed-surface border rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors text-center">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Object Catalog</p>
          <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">Explore the pattern through physical objects.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="themed-border border-t my-16"></div>

    <!-- Technical Section Header -->
    <section class="mb-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 themed-text-muted">The Technical Details</h2>
      <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">You don't need this to see the pattern. But if you're curious about the notation:</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Identity -->
    <section class="mb-12 text-center">
      <div class="themed-surface border rounded-lg p-8 mb-6">
        <p class="text-2xl font-mono mb-4">e<sup>iπ</sup> + 1 = 0</p>
        <p class="themed-text-muted">Euler's Identity — Contrast, Rotation, Closure in five symbols</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Six Constants (Collapsible) -->
    <details class="mb-8">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer themed-text-muted hover:opacity-80 mb-4 text-center">The Six Constants ▾</summary>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
        <div class="themed-surface border rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">0</p>
          <p class="themed-text-muted">玄 xuán</p>
          <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">unoccupiable center</p>
        </div>
        <div class="themed-surface border rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">1</p>
          <p class="themed-text-muted">有 yǒu</p>
          <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">structural unity</p>
        </div>
        <div class="themed-surface border rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">i</p>
          <p class="themed-text-muted">名 míng</p>
          <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">orthogonal distinction</p>
        </div>
        <div class="themed-surface border rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">e</p>
          <p class="themed-text-muted">相生 xiāng shēng</p>
          <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">mutual generation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="themed-surface border rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">π</p>
          <p class="themed-text-muted">(measure)</p>
          <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">closure of curvature</p>
        </div>
        <div class="themed-surface border rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">φ</p>
          <p class="themed-text-muted">常 cháng</p>
          <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">derived from frame-invariance</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Operator Grammar (Collapsible) -->
    <details class="mb-12">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer themed-text-muted hover:opacity-80 mb-4 text-center">DDJ Operator Grammar ▾</summary>
      <div class="themed-surface border rounded-lg p-6 mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-left">
          <thead>
            <tr class="themed-border border-b">
              <th class="pb-3">DDJ</th>
              <th class="pb-3">Math</th>
              <th class="pb-3">Function</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="themed-text-secondary">
            <tr class="themed-border-light border-b">
              <td class="py-2">名 míng</td>
              <td class="font-mono">i</td>
              <td>orthogonal cut</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="themed-border-light border-b">
              <td class="py-2">利₁ lì</td>
              <td class="font-mono">e<sup>iπ</sup> = −1</td>
              <td>boundary-creating cut</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="themed-border-light border-b">
              <td class="py-2">反 fǎn</td>
              <td class="font-mono">+1</td>
              <td>return to equilibrium</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="themed-border-light border-b">
              <td class="py-2">相生 xiāng shēng</td>
              <td class="font-mono">e</td>
              <td>mutual generation</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-2">無為 wú wéi</td>
              <td class="font-mono">∂P/∂t = 0</td>
              <td>paradox preservation</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Documentation Links -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-center themed-text-muted">Full Documentation</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/docset/rsm_complete.html" class="block themed-surface border rounded-lg p-4 transition-colors">
          <p class="font-bold text-sm">RSM v0.986</p>
          <p class="text-xs themed-text-muted">The complete formal framework</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docset/current/" class="block themed-surface border rounded-lg p-4 transition-colors">
          <p class="font-bold text-sm">Individual Docset Files</p>
          <p class="text-xs themed-text-muted">Browse all audited documents</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-center themed-text-muted text-sm themed-border border-t pt-8">
      <p class="italic mb-2">Pattern, not proof.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Every frame accurate, none final—return to pattern.</p>
      <p>Will Goldstein & Claude — RSM v0.986 — December 2025</p>
    </footer>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
